WEBVTT

01:39.240 --> 01:40.840
Dear Yueming,

01:40.960 --> 01:42.600
I've read the letter

01:42.600 --> 01:44.460
you sent from Beijing many times.

01:44.840 --> 01:46.080
You witnessed

01:46.080 --> 01:48.479
the founding of New China with your own eyes,

01:48.479 --> 01:50.280
and saw everyone smiling,

01:50.280 --> 01:52.039
smiling so happily.

01:53.160 --> 01:55.680
You said your teacher assigned an essay

01:55.880 --> 01:58.160
titled 'My Country and My Home',

01:58.440 --> 02:00.970
and you wanted to hear the story of our family.

02:03.160 --> 02:04.920
Where should I begin?

02:06.280 --> 02:06.600
Yueming,

02:06.600 --> 02:07.520
you know

02:07.600 --> 02:09.039
you have two fathers.

02:09.639 --> 02:11.840
One gave you life,

02:12.160 --> 02:13.200
and the other

02:13.520 --> 02:15.480
protected you with his life.

02:15.920 --> 02:17.120
You also know

02:17.520 --> 02:19.120
that on the day you were born,

02:19.280 --> 02:22.760
China fell into its darkest night.

02:24.160 --> 02:26.920
You experienced a little of that history,

02:27.200 --> 02:30.480
but there are still many parts you have not heard of.

02:31.120 --> 02:34.400
I have the responsibility to tell you

02:35.000 --> 02:37.060
this history exactly as it happened.

02:37.880 --> 02:39.120
The journey of our family

02:39.120 --> 02:41.050
is walking alongside the country,

02:41.120 --> 02:42.880
from the deepest night,

02:42.880 --> 02:46.000
mile by mile, until dawn.

02:46.680 --> 02:50.160
This long story of eight thousand miles,

02:50.600 --> 02:52.520
let's start from the dawn of

02:52.520 --> 02:55.480
the spring of 1944.

02:55.480 --> 02:56.480
Fellow villagers,

02:56.480 --> 02:57.640
let's hurry up.

03:20.520 --> 03:22.079
We are currently in this position.

03:22.079 --> 03:23.680
The enemy might come in and out from here.

03:23.680 --> 03:24.720
We can deploy from here.

03:24.720 --> 03:26.980
Reporting to the Regimental Commander,

03:27.000 --> 03:28.260
Meng Wanfu reporting.

03:32.840 --> 03:33.920
Meng Wanfu.

03:36.960 --> 03:37.690
Take the gun.

03:38.360 --> 03:39.040
Come,

03:39.200 --> 03:39.960
give it to me.

03:44.240 --> 03:45.160
Good brother.

03:48.040 --> 03:50.800
Commander, Meng Wanfu has returned to the unit.

03:51.920 --> 03:54.520
Brigade Commander, Regimental Commander.

03:55.120 --> 03:57.560
Zhang Dougui, Zhang Yunkui.

03:59.280 --> 04:01.680
Kong Erbao, He Bishi.

04:02.120 --> 04:05.160
Zhang Yunkui, Meng Wanfu.

04:07.080 --> 04:08.940
It feels like a seven-year dream.

04:09.160 --> 04:11.240
Yes, just like a dream.

04:13.760 --> 04:14.600
Yueming,

04:14.800 --> 04:16.680
in the summer of 1937,

04:16.959 --> 04:18.959
you were still in my belly.

04:19.240 --> 04:23.720
At that time, the War of Resistance Against Japanese Aggression had just fully broken out.

04:23.720 --> 04:25.360
The Communist Party of China called for

04:25.360 --> 04:28.160
the establishment of an anti-Japanese national united front,

04:28.160 --> 04:32.080
emphasizing the mobilization of all national forces to resist aggression.

04:32.080 --> 04:35.200
The Chinese nation united as never before.

04:35.440 --> 04:38.600
The Nationalist Government also made military deployments.

04:38.600 --> 04:40.040
Your father Yunkui

04:40.120 --> 04:42.600
hadn't been home for several months.

05:18.280 --> 05:21.160
Sister-in-law Liu, did you hear?

05:49.280 --> 05:50.080
A Yi,

05:50.360 --> 05:51.320
the young master is back.

05:51.320 --> 05:51.780
Really?

05:51.920 --> 05:52.640
Quick,

05:52.640 --> 05:54.120
I need to make some of the young master's favorite food.

05:54.120 --> 05:54.720
Hurry up.

05:54.800 --> 05:55.520
Okay.

06:06.640 --> 06:07.320
Father,

06:07.840 --> 06:08.760
I'm back.

06:19.840 --> 06:22.480
Compared to Yan Lugong, what is

06:23.560 --> 06:25.280
Zhao Zi'ang lacking?

06:25.920 --> 06:27.240
My calligraphy skills are lacking,

06:27.240 --> 06:29.640
I only know that handwriting reflects the person,

06:29.640 --> 06:32.040
and Zhao Zi'ang lacks unwavering integrity.

06:32.040 --> 06:34.480
That's what Kang Youwei and his ilk say.

06:35.120 --> 06:38.050
'Do not emulate the decadent style of Zhao and Dong.'

06:38.159 --> 06:39.490
The words aren't wrong.

06:39.600 --> 06:42.130
But did Kang Youwei understand calligraphy?

06:42.240 --> 06:43.760
What big words.

06:44.520 --> 06:46.760
Yes. Please teach me, Father.

06:47.040 --> 06:48.560
Zhao Zi'ang was talented.

06:51.720 --> 06:52.720
A talented person

06:53.440 --> 06:55.120
can protect themselves

06:55.680 --> 06:58.240
and those around them.

06:58.920 --> 07:00.250
A person of great talent

07:00.640 --> 07:02.640
can preserve the cultural lineage.

07:04.200 --> 07:07.120
But Yan Lugong had spirit.

07:07.560 --> 07:08.240
Talent and spirit,

07:08.240 --> 07:10.480
the two words are worlds apart.

07:10.960 --> 07:13.440
From beginning to end,

07:13.640 --> 07:16.680
Yan Lugong used the center of the brush, vigorous and independent,

07:16.680 --> 07:18.640
sharp and unyielding,

07:18.680 --> 07:20.360
intending to write for all people in the world

07:20.360 --> 07:22.880
the word 'manhood'.

07:23.400 --> 07:26.480
So although he had no intention of becoming a calligrapher,

07:26.480 --> 07:31.120
he was revered as a master for all generations.

07:32.040 --> 07:33.040
I understand.

07:34.560 --> 07:36.240
Why did you come back today?

07:36.360 --> 07:38.480
I was appointed as the major general commander of the 87th Brigade.

07:38.480 --> 07:39.480
I need to rush to Shanghai immediately

07:39.480 --> 07:40.740
to prepare for battle.

08:18.760 --> 08:20.280
The Nationalist Government,

08:20.280 --> 08:22.120
even at this stage,

08:22.520 --> 08:25.320
still pins its hopes on international mediation.

08:25.720 --> 08:27.360
Leaving things to chance

08:27.440 --> 08:28.640
is not advisable.

08:29.000 --> 08:30.800
The September 18th Incident in the Northeast,

08:30.800 --> 08:32.360
Shanghai five years ago.

08:32.440 --> 08:34.440
Haven't we suffered enough losses?

08:34.720 --> 08:36.400
On the contrary, the Communist Party's

08:36.400 --> 08:37.880
'August 1st Declaration'

08:37.960 --> 08:39.480
is more visionary.

08:39.640 --> 08:41.159
Have you read it?

08:41.320 --> 08:42.280
I have, Father.

08:42.799 --> 08:44.600
They call on the whole nation to implement the war of resistance

08:44.600 --> 08:45.920
and resist foreign aggression.

08:45.920 --> 08:47.440
It's very inspiring to me.

08:47.560 --> 08:49.090
I also agree with this idea.

08:49.680 --> 08:51.200
You are absolutely right.

08:51.360 --> 08:53.320
Unite the national united front,

08:53.800 --> 08:55.160
resist aggression,

08:55.200 --> 08:56.400
take the initiative,

08:56.920 --> 08:59.580
and drive the Japanese out of the Huangpu River.

08:59.720 --> 09:00.960
How can we not win?

09:02.080 --> 09:03.940
How can the enemy not be defeated?

09:04.440 --> 09:06.200
Then again,

09:06.640 --> 09:09.160
how can we be sure of victory?

09:09.720 --> 09:12.040
It is just to be fearless.

09:12.840 --> 09:14.040
So,

09:14.040 --> 09:16.170
we still need to cultivate our spirit.

09:16.360 --> 09:17.620
You are right, Father.

09:18.880 --> 09:19.680
Come.

09:27.920 --> 09:28.720
Coming.

09:32.000 --> 09:33.660
Come, Buns, serve the dishes.

09:33.960 --> 09:34.960
Coming.

09:37.640 --> 09:39.080
Flavored eggplant.

09:39.240 --> 09:40.720
Here we go.

10:01.160 --> 10:01.840
Brother.

10:02.320 --> 10:04.780
You look so happy when you have a happy event.

10:04.800 --> 10:06.160
You are a bridegroom now.

10:06.160 --> 10:07.840
Your smile reaches your ears.

10:08.400 --> 10:09.120
Buns.

10:09.640 --> 10:11.170
I just ask you one question.

10:11.680 --> 10:12.720
How do I look?

10:12.880 --> 10:14.720
My brother is a human.

10:15.920 --> 10:17.080
What do you know?

10:17.640 --> 10:19.700
Horse dung looks good on the outside,

10:20.360 --> 10:22.000
but it's full of chaff inside.

10:22.000 --> 10:22.840
For a person,

10:23.040 --> 10:25.170
the most important thing is two words.

10:25.400 --> 10:26.120
What?

10:26.160 --> 10:27.760
Food and clothing.

10:28.440 --> 10:29.320
Brothers.

10:30.080 --> 10:31.210
What about one word?

10:31.240 --> 10:32.360
Food.

10:32.840 --> 10:33.640
Bah.

10:33.720 --> 10:34.760
It's money.

10:36.520 --> 10:37.880
Sir.

10:38.720 --> 10:40.720
We are going to the battlefield tomorrow.

10:40.720 --> 10:41.560
Yes, yes.

10:41.560 --> 10:43.320
We just want to eat some meat today.

10:43.320 --> 10:44.000
Eat meat.

10:44.400 --> 10:46.240
You just give us this.

10:46.920 --> 10:48.360
Sir, let me tell you.

10:48.440 --> 10:49.440
Now the price of meat

10:49.440 --> 10:50.680
changes every day.

10:50.840 --> 10:52.160
It rises faster

10:52.280 --> 10:53.480
than the Japanese planes.

10:53.480 --> 10:54.360
Fly even faster.

10:54.360 --> 10:56.840
And the key is that there is nowhere to buy it.

10:56.880 --> 10:57.810
I'm telling you.

10:58.120 --> 10:58.880
Four eggs.

10:59.000 --> 11:00.880
I'll make some egg soup

11:00.880 --> 11:02.210
for you four gentlemen.

11:02.320 --> 11:04.120
With extra wood ear mushrooms and vermicelli.

11:04.120 --> 11:04.520
Extra.

11:06.080 --> 11:07.240
You look down on us, don't you?

11:07.240 --> 11:07.880
No.

11:07.920 --> 11:08.920
No, sir.

11:09.000 --> 11:09.560
Listen to me.

11:09.560 --> 11:11.200
We risk our lives

11:11.240 --> 11:12.240
to defend our country.

11:12.240 --> 11:12.960
For who?

11:13.080 --> 11:13.600
For who?

11:13.680 --> 11:14.480
For you.

11:14.600 --> 11:15.920
For me.

11:16.360 --> 11:17.240
You are too greedy.

11:17.240 --> 11:18.440
No.

11:18.520 --> 11:19.280
Cut the crap.

11:19.320 --> 11:19.800
Beef.

11:19.840 --> 11:20.970
Do you have it or not?

11:21.680 --> 11:22.600
Sir.

11:22.640 --> 11:23.760
I really don't have it.

11:23.760 --> 11:24.400
Really not.

11:24.400 --> 11:25.560
We really don't have any.

11:25.560 --> 11:27.160
I wouldn't dare lie.

11:30.720 --> 11:31.780
What are you doing?

11:32.720 --> 11:33.320
Officers.

11:33.360 --> 11:33.960
Brothers,

11:34.000 --> 11:34.400
stop.

11:34.480 --> 11:35.800
We're eating meat today.

11:35.800 --> 11:37.840
Pork belly or ribs?

11:37.880 --> 11:38.480
Why don't you choose?

11:38.480 --> 11:39.240
Don't.

11:39.560 --> 11:41.560
Don't waste time with him. Smash it.

11:42.640 --> 11:45.360
Chinese don't fight Chinese.

11:46.040 --> 11:47.600
Officers.

11:47.680 --> 11:48.320
Officers,

11:48.520 --> 11:49.160
calm down.

11:49.280 --> 11:49.880
Calm down.

11:49.880 --> 11:51.880
Don't fight.

11:51.960 --> 11:52.560
Calm down.

11:52.600 --> 11:53.560
Calm down.

11:53.720 --> 11:54.440
Calm down.

11:56.960 --> 11:57.560
Officer, have mercy.

11:57.560 --> 11:58.680
Officers.

11:58.720 --> 11:59.440
Calm down. Have mercy.

11:59.440 --> 12:00.080
Calm down.

12:00.160 --> 12:00.840
Calm down.

12:01.120 --> 12:02.120
Please calm down.

12:02.120 --> 12:02.960
Come,

12:04.160 --> 12:05.160
have a cigarette.

12:06.320 --> 12:06.800
Have a cigarette.

12:06.800 --> 12:08.200
Yes, have a cigarette.

12:08.320 --> 12:09.320
Have a cigarette.

12:09.320 --> 12:10.440
Officer,

12:10.520 --> 12:12.080
here, have a smoke.

12:12.120 --> 12:12.760
Have a cigarette.

12:12.760 --> 12:13.960
Come, calm down.

12:14.800 --> 12:16.330
Officer, have a cigarette.

12:17.600 --> 12:18.960
Here, Officer.

12:19.040 --> 12:19.840
I don't smoke.

12:20.560 --> 12:21.840
Just take it anyway.

12:21.920 --> 12:22.520
Take it.

12:22.760 --> 12:23.400
Take it.

12:24.880 --> 12:26.360
This officer is right.

12:26.680 --> 12:27.940
To defend the country,

12:28.080 --> 12:29.210
you provide the men,

12:29.400 --> 12:31.360
we naturally provide the meat.

12:31.480 --> 12:33.280
Isn't it written on the slogan outside?

12:33.280 --> 12:34.840
Everyone is responsible

12:35.160 --> 12:37.360
for the rise and fall of the country, including the cooks.

12:37.360 --> 12:38.560
Including the cooks.

12:41.320 --> 12:43.240
Don't be angry, Officers.

12:43.520 --> 12:45.320
You just want to eat meat, right?

12:45.880 --> 12:47.240
No problem.

12:52.280 --> 12:53.320
No problem.

12:54.520 --> 12:55.560
No problem.

12:56.640 --> 12:58.440
The officers just want to eat meat, right?

12:58.440 --> 12:59.160
Whether there is meat,

12:59.160 --> 13:00.680
how would the Manager know?

13:00.680 --> 13:01.000
Right,

13:01.000 --> 13:02.680
naturally the cooks know.

13:03.080 --> 13:03.880
There is meat.

13:04.120 --> 13:04.920
There is meat.

13:05.080 --> 13:06.360
There's definitely meat.

13:06.360 --> 13:07.560
It's coming right up.

13:07.720 --> 13:09.320
Officers, have a snack first.

13:09.320 --> 13:10.440
The meat is coming right up.

13:10.440 --> 13:11.640
Officer, please sit.

13:12.080 --> 13:13.280
The meat is coming right up.

13:13.280 --> 13:14.440
The meat is coming right up.

13:14.440 --> 13:15.800
Please sit.

13:15.840 --> 13:16.500
Please sit.

13:21.440 --> 13:22.500
Have a snack first.

13:22.680 --> 13:24.210
The meat is coming right up.

13:24.400 --> 13:25.200
Please wait a moment.

13:25.200 --> 13:26.280
Please wait a moment.

13:26.280 --> 13:26.960
Beef.

13:28.160 --> 13:29.000
Must be beef.

13:30.600 --> 13:31.400
And soup?

13:32.960 --> 13:34.160
Serve it all together.

13:34.160 --> 13:35.420
Serve it all together.

13:42.480 --> 13:43.280
Brat.

13:43.960 --> 13:44.890
You startled me.

13:45.920 --> 13:48.000
The beef I bought just this morning

13:48.040 --> 13:49.120
is gone by noon.

13:49.560 --> 13:51.420
Did you steal it, you little brat?

13:51.560 --> 13:52.880
Manager, how is that possible?

13:52.880 --> 13:55.200
You even took my cigarettes to treat others.

13:55.200 --> 13:56.040
Give me the cigarettes.

13:56.040 --> 13:56.960
I don't have any.

13:56.960 --> 13:57.760
I don't.

13:58.320 --> 13:59.000
Don't move.

13:59.240 --> 14:00.300
I didn't take them.

14:00.360 --> 14:01.000
Gone.

14:01.040 --> 14:02.080
Gone.

14:02.160 --> 14:02.720
Look.

14:03.000 --> 14:03.600
There's more.

14:03.600 --> 14:03.960
Gone.

14:03.960 --> 14:05.120
Turn around.

14:05.320 --> 14:06.160
Really gone.

14:07.920 --> 14:09.560
You hid quite a lot.

14:09.800 --> 14:10.480
You brat.

14:10.480 --> 14:12.080
I wasn't treating them.

14:12.160 --> 14:13.200
I was helping you out of a jam,

14:13.200 --> 14:14.440
so I deserve this.

14:14.600 --> 14:15.600
Now you've taken them all.

14:15.600 --> 14:17.240
Search me, there's nothing left.

14:17.240 --> 14:18.240
Turn around again.

14:18.240 --> 14:19.120
Turn around.

14:19.920 --> 14:20.920
What is this?

14:21.240 --> 14:22.400
Manager.

14:22.440 --> 14:23.280
You can't touch this.

14:23.280 --> 14:24.280
You can't touch this.

14:24.280 --> 14:25.040
I'll show you.

14:25.040 --> 14:25.880
I'll show you.

14:25.920 --> 14:27.120
Give it to me, show it to me.

14:27.120 --> 14:28.320
I'll show you.

14:29.960 --> 14:32.880
This is the money I've saved for three years for my marriage.

14:32.880 --> 14:34.200
I have nothing besides this.

14:34.200 --> 14:35.260
Come on, search me.

14:35.280 --> 14:35.920
Search.

14:36.000 --> 14:37.330
I won't search anymore.

14:37.440 --> 14:38.800
The beef is gone anyway.

14:38.960 --> 14:41.020
Aren't you playing the generous guy?

14:41.040 --> 14:42.800
Tomorrow, for the meat at your banquet,

14:42.800 --> 14:43.560
I'll use it.

14:43.600 --> 14:44.000
Xizi.

14:44.200 --> 14:44.720
Don't.

14:44.760 --> 14:45.360
Did you hear me?

14:45.360 --> 14:45.760
Don't.

14:45.760 --> 14:46.560
Take his meat.

14:46.560 --> 14:47.720
Why are you joining the fun?

14:47.720 --> 14:48.200
Get lost.

14:48.200 --> 14:49.360
Get out of the way.

14:50.720 --> 14:51.400
No, Manager.

14:51.400 --> 14:52.200
If you do this,

14:52.280 --> 14:53.740
you might as well cut me up.

14:53.760 --> 14:54.360
Cut me, come on.

14:54.360 --> 14:55.000
Come on.

14:55.080 --> 14:56.520
What's the use of cutting you?

14:56.520 --> 14:58.400
Those people up front are still waiting.

14:58.400 --> 14:59.800
Then how do we solve this?

15:00.240 --> 15:01.840
I've already figured it out.

15:05.480 --> 15:06.240
What is this?

15:07.360 --> 15:08.720
Those soldiers

15:08.760 --> 15:11.440
have definitely never eaten this Castanopsis tofu.

15:11.440 --> 15:13.480
I'll cut this tofu into slices,

15:13.480 --> 15:15.680
then fry it thoroughly in oil,

15:15.840 --> 15:17.360
until it's crispy and wrinkled.

15:17.360 --> 15:19.080
Add some chili and beef tallow,

15:19.080 --> 15:20.440
and once the tofu flavor is gone,

15:20.440 --> 15:21.880
tell them it's beef;

15:21.880 --> 15:24.280
they won't be able to taste the difference.

15:24.440 --> 15:25.360
Can you make it?

15:25.760 --> 15:26.680
I'll stir-fry it in a bit,

15:26.680 --> 15:28.140
and you can taste it first.

15:28.240 --> 15:28.920
Okay.

15:30.400 --> 15:31.480
Do as you said.

15:36.040 --> 15:37.880
Keep your hands clean.

15:38.400 --> 15:39.240
Manager.

15:39.320 --> 15:41.040
We are innocent.

15:41.160 --> 15:41.880
You guys.

15:43.920 --> 15:44.520
Manager.

15:44.560 --> 15:45.160
Miss Xiaoyue.

15:45.160 --> 15:46.240
Have some wedding candies.

15:46.240 --> 15:47.640
Remember to come tomorrow.

15:47.640 --> 15:48.440
Of course.

15:48.880 --> 15:49.940
Congratulations.

15:55.400 --> 15:57.200
Sikui, come, have some candies.

15:57.400 --> 15:57.880
Congratulations.

15:57.880 --> 15:58.600
Come tomorrow.

15:58.600 --> 15:59.360
Congratulations, Miss Xiaoyue.

15:59.360 --> 16:00.000
Thank you.

16:00.560 --> 16:01.960
Erwa, have some candies.

16:02.440 --> 16:02.960
Thank you.

16:02.960 --> 16:03.400
Come tomorrow.

16:03.400 --> 16:04.360
Congratulations.

16:04.360 --> 16:05.000
Xiao Li.

16:05.040 --> 16:06.500
Okay, thank you, Xiaoyue.

16:06.600 --> 16:07.400
Come.

16:07.560 --> 16:08.490
Xiaoyue is here.

16:08.800 --> 16:09.860
Congratulations.

16:10.560 --> 16:11.440
Buns.

16:12.160 --> 16:12.800
You must all come tomorrow,

16:12.800 --> 16:13.160
none of you can be missing.

16:13.160 --> 16:13.960
We will definitely come.

16:13.960 --> 16:15.160
Come, have some candies.

16:15.160 --> 16:16.560
So pretty and diligent.

16:16.880 --> 16:17.640
Thank you, Miss Xiaoyue.

16:17.640 --> 16:19.440
I don't know what good deeds Brother Wanfu did in his past life

16:19.440 --> 16:20.900
to have such good fortune.

16:21.600 --> 16:22.840
Brothers, tell me,

16:23.200 --> 16:24.240
when can I marry

16:24.240 --> 16:25.200
such a wife?

16:25.400 --> 16:26.200
You?

16:27.880 --> 16:29.080
You'll never marry one.

16:29.080 --> 16:30.400
You sure have a sweet mouth.

16:30.400 --> 16:32.640
I'll reward you with two more cups of wedding wine tomorrow.

16:32.640 --> 16:33.560
It's a deal.

16:34.960 --> 16:36.360
Weren't you following Miss Yu

16:36.360 --> 16:38.200
to the anti-Japanese benefit performance?

16:38.200 --> 16:39.800
Why did you come back so soon?

16:39.880 --> 16:41.210
After the performance,

16:41.440 --> 16:43.360
Young Master Luo took the lady away.

16:43.360 --> 16:44.600
They went on a date.

16:44.600 --> 16:45.640
So I came back.

16:46.280 --> 16:46.960
Come.

16:51.840 --> 16:52.960
Is it sweet?

16:53.480 --> 16:54.200
Sweet.

16:54.840 --> 16:56.040
I'll go clean up then.

16:59.320 --> 17:00.080
Come back.

17:09.160 --> 17:10.089
Open your mouth.

17:18.160 --> 17:19.220
Does it smell good?

17:22.040 --> 17:22.839
No.

17:47.320 --> 17:48.360
These words

17:49.200 --> 17:51.000
I wrote specially for you.

17:52.240 --> 17:54.300
Do you remember where they came from?

17:54.440 --> 17:55.880
'Every branch and leaf concerns our feelings'.

17:55.880 --> 17:56.800
Zheng Banqiao's

17:56.800 --> 17:58.400
'Painting Bamboo in the Weixian Office and Presenting It to Uncle

17:58.400 --> 17:59.680
Bao Kuo'.

17:59.920 --> 18:01.800
Father wants me to keep my duty in mind,

18:01.800 --> 18:03.120
no matter when and where,

18:03.120 --> 18:05.980
always bearing in mind the suffering of the people.

18:06.200 --> 18:07.080
Good.

18:11.240 --> 18:12.480
Come out, Yujiao.

18:12.800 --> 18:14.520
I saw you a long time ago.

18:17.360 --> 18:18.440
Father.

18:26.680 --> 18:28.360
Go and

18:28.560 --> 18:30.480
have a good talk with Yujiao.

18:31.440 --> 18:32.640
It's not easy for her.

18:40.280 --> 18:41.280
I almost forgot.

18:42.840 --> 18:43.680
Father.

18:43.880 --> 18:45.880
Specially to treat your joint pain.

18:47.000 --> 18:47.720
Report.

18:52.560 --> 18:53.800
Brigade Commander, urgent order from the division headquarters.

18:53.800 --> 18:54.920
Please return to your unit immediately,

18:54.920 --> 18:56.650
the troops will set off at once.

19:19.760 --> 19:20.560
Father.

19:22.480 --> 19:23.810
Your son is going to war.

20:10.280 --> 20:11.160
Mrs. Liu.

20:12.120 --> 20:13.040
Mrs. Liu.

20:14.280 --> 20:15.240
Mrs. Liu.

20:16.280 --> 20:17.240
Mrs. Liu.

20:18.200 --> 20:19.200
Mrs. Liu, help me.

20:19.360 --> 20:20.040
Coming.

20:20.120 --> 20:21.520
Help me. Hurry up.

20:21.760 --> 20:22.820
You're not eating?

20:22.960 --> 20:23.880
Take it easy.

20:24.240 --> 20:24.880
Come.

20:27.840 --> 20:29.040
Let me pour it for you.

20:29.200 --> 20:29.400
Pour it in.

20:29.400 --> 20:30.240
No rush.

20:30.320 --> 20:31.560
Okay, come.

20:31.760 --> 20:32.400
Pour it in.

20:33.200 --> 20:34.520
It's 622 pieces, right?

20:34.520 --> 20:35.780
Yes, they're all here.

21:01.680 --> 21:03.720
Here is one more.

21:06.720 --> 21:07.480
It's raining.

21:07.480 --> 21:08.880
Madam, take an umbrella.

21:09.240 --> 21:11.900
Madam, you're pregnant. Be careful not to slip.

24:03.480 --> 24:04.610
Eat before you work.

24:04.760 --> 24:06.020
I made you some egg tea.

24:06.560 --> 24:07.600
It clears the internal heat.

24:07.600 --> 24:08.360
Come here.

24:09.800 --> 24:10.600
What's wrong?

24:13.720 --> 24:15.720
Look at my invention.

24:18.360 --> 24:19.200
It moves.

24:20.240 --> 24:21.280
Is it sturdy?

24:21.320 --> 24:22.160
Try it.

24:27.640 --> 24:28.970
It can actually do this.

24:31.080 --> 24:32.560
What are you wearing tomorrow?

24:32.560 --> 24:33.920
Do you want to borrow

24:33.960 --> 24:35.560
Young Master Luo's student uniform from Miss?

24:35.560 --> 24:37.160
I've already paid the deposit for the mandarin jacket.

24:37.160 --> 24:38.720
I'll go pick it up in a bit.

24:39.240 --> 24:39.840
Besides,

24:39.840 --> 24:42.080
no groom wears a student uniform.

24:43.400 --> 24:44.200
Han Xiaoyue,

24:44.800 --> 24:46.520
do you just like students?

24:47.160 --> 24:49.120
Why would I like students?

24:49.480 --> 24:52.120
I just like people who are more literate.

24:53.080 --> 24:54.560
More literate?

24:55.360 --> 24:56.890
We aren't even married yet,

24:57.320 --> 25:00.560
and you already dislike that I don't know many words, right?

25:00.560 --> 25:01.440
Let me tell you,

25:02.840 --> 25:04.680
even if I don't know many words,

25:06.080 --> 25:07.940
I still bought you a gold hairpin.

25:14.320 --> 25:15.480
It's beautifully made.

25:15.480 --> 25:16.240
Wanfu.

25:16.960 --> 25:17.840
I heard

25:18.640 --> 25:21.080
the Japanese army has arrived on the Huangpu River.

25:21.080 --> 25:22.810
Are they really going to fight?

25:23.000 --> 25:25.120
Can we still hold our wedding banquet?

25:25.120 --> 25:26.800
Why are you worrying about this?

25:26.800 --> 25:27.660
The higher-ups

25:28.320 --> 25:30.720
say it's a critical moment,

25:31.600 --> 25:33.360
and war is inevitable.

25:34.080 --> 25:35.200
But by night,

25:35.360 --> 25:36.760
they changed their tune,

25:37.720 --> 25:40.450
saying there's still a glimmer of hope for peace,

25:40.840 --> 25:42.100
and they won't give up.

25:43.280 --> 25:45.160
They flip-flop like pancakes.

25:45.520 --> 25:47.280
Flipping back and forth.

25:47.320 --> 25:49.400
They're not even as good as a cook like me.

25:49.400 --> 25:50.280
Don't worry.

25:50.320 --> 25:52.850
If the sky falls, the tall ones will hold it up.

25:53.920 --> 25:56.780
It's not something us ordinary people can control.

25:58.560 --> 25:59.290
Give it to me.

26:03.880 --> 26:04.740
Wash your face.

26:05.280 --> 26:07.140
Washing my face isn't important.

26:07.360 --> 26:09.040
There's no rush.

26:09.720 --> 26:11.360
I want to try

26:11.640 --> 26:13.840
Miss Han's invention.

26:22.720 --> 26:23.520
Comfortable.

26:24.160 --> 26:24.920
Xiaoyue.

26:26.440 --> 26:29.400
Here in Shanghai,

26:30.840 --> 26:32.320
we finally have a home.

26:37.200 --> 26:38.040
Miss Han,

26:39.960 --> 26:41.800
please come quickly

26:41.880 --> 26:43.520
to Mr. Meng,

26:43.600 --> 26:45.800
who can afford a gold hairpin.

26:49.160 --> 26:50.400
Come on.

27:06.160 --> 27:06.690
Let's go.

27:09.560 --> 27:14.240
The crescent moon shines over many provinces.

27:14.360 --> 27:18.640
Some families rejoice, some sorrow.

27:19.000 --> 27:23.360
Some couples share a silken bed.

27:23.760 --> 27:27.640
Some are scattered in other provinces.

27:28.040 --> 27:29.960
Fight to the end.

27:29.960 --> 27:32.160
Unite as one.

27:32.160 --> 27:32.720
Down with them.

27:32.720 --> 27:34.880
Congratulations, sir.

27:35.000 --> 27:36.160
Victory in the war of resistance.

27:36.160 --> 27:37.090
You startled me.

27:37.200 --> 27:38.400
I have no spare money.

27:38.840 --> 27:40.840
I, Huang the psychic, travel far and wide,

27:40.840 --> 27:42.360
relying on my knowledge of astronomy above,

27:42.360 --> 27:43.360
geography below,

27:43.480 --> 27:45.000
understanding the universe,

27:45.000 --> 27:46.280
and balancing yin and yang.

27:46.280 --> 27:47.340
But never on money.

27:47.560 --> 27:48.600
I'll give you three pieces of advice

27:48.600 --> 27:49.640
for free.

27:51.160 --> 27:53.620
Sir, you have a great joyful event coming up.

27:54.520 --> 27:56.440
I have joy, you have joy.

27:56.480 --> 27:57.960
There are plenty of people on this street with joy.

27:57.960 --> 27:59.240
I can read fortunes too.

27:59.240 --> 28:02.040
Sir, you have a lady on your mind.

28:04.080 --> 28:05.520
An Anhui lady.

28:11.680 --> 28:13.810
Sir, you lack a bit of literary talent,

28:14.040 --> 28:15.840
making a living with your craft.

28:21.520 --> 28:22.650
That doesn't count.

28:22.760 --> 28:24.220
You still owe me one. Go on.

28:25.040 --> 28:27.000
The lowest level of physiognomy looks at bones,

28:27.000 --> 28:28.640
the middle at complexion,

28:28.680 --> 28:30.360
the highest at voice.

28:31.280 --> 28:34.000
Sir, your voice is as dry as fire,

28:34.000 --> 28:35.320
running around with no support.

28:35.320 --> 28:36.850
Your tone is inauspicious.

28:37.280 --> 28:40.240
Although you're rushing toward a great joy now,

28:40.400 --> 28:43.080
you're unaware of impending disaster.

28:43.320 --> 28:46.160
You'll surely face imprisonment.

28:51.280 --> 28:52.320
Let me tell you.

28:52.480 --> 28:53.840
If you had met me yesterday

28:53.840 --> 28:55.080
and said something like this,

28:55.080 --> 28:56.880
I would've slapped you already.

28:56.960 --> 28:58.020
Stop following me.

28:59.280 --> 29:00.000
Sir.

29:00.120 --> 29:02.120
Our meeting today

29:02.120 --> 29:02.440
Go.

29:02.440 --> 29:04.000
is a tremendous destiny.

29:04.160 --> 29:07.090
Since it's fate, I must help you resolve this crisis.

29:07.400 --> 29:09.320
If my calculations are correct,

29:09.320 --> 29:10.800
the items in your bag

29:10.800 --> 29:14.480
must be the clothes for your joyous occasion.

29:16.400 --> 29:17.400
Right?

29:19.120 --> 29:19.920
Metal,

29:20.320 --> 29:21.840
metal, wood, water, fire.

29:22.000 --> 29:23.160
Fire, wood, metal.

29:25.400 --> 29:29.400
And jewelry worn by women.

29:29.920 --> 29:30.760
You brat.

29:31.480 --> 29:33.760
You've been following me all the way, haven't you?

29:33.760 --> 29:36.640
Everything is predestined in the unseen world.

29:38.160 --> 29:40.640
However, sir, your voice is resonant.

29:41.000 --> 29:43.160
This crisis can still be resolved.

29:45.040 --> 29:46.880
You must first pray to Lord Guan.

29:48.720 --> 29:49.720
Pray to Lord Guan?

29:50.600 --> 29:52.930
Then I have to give donation money, right?

29:53.360 --> 29:54.120
Alright.

30:00.840 --> 30:02.160
You're not blind.

30:04.960 --> 30:05.820
Let me tell you.

30:05.960 --> 30:08.320
I don't believe in fate.

30:08.440 --> 30:09.770
I only believe in money.

30:10.080 --> 30:11.160
If I believed you,

30:11.200 --> 30:13.160
I would have changed my fate long ago.

30:13.160 --> 30:14.160
Don't bother me again,

30:14.160 --> 30:15.320
or I'll really slap you.

30:15.320 --> 30:16.200
Get lost.

30:17.240 --> 30:19.200
A gentleman doesn't stand under a dangerous wall.

30:19.200 --> 30:21.520
If you don't listen to me, you'll suffer a disaster.

30:21.520 --> 30:22.160
Who is it?

30:24.920 --> 30:25.760
Let go of me!

30:27.280 --> 30:27.920
Kill.

30:28.160 --> 30:28.640
One.

30:28.680 --> 30:29.360
Kill.

30:29.440 --> 30:30.040
Two.

30:30.120 --> 30:30.920
Kill.

30:31.000 --> 30:31.600
One.

30:31.720 --> 30:32.400
Kill.

30:34.440 --> 30:35.120
Everyone, get out of the car!

30:35.120 --> 30:35.760
Get out!

30:35.840 --> 30:36.320
Get out!

30:36.360 --> 30:38.280
Those in the carriage, get inside quickly.

30:38.280 --> 30:38.840
Go!

30:38.920 --> 30:40.920
What are you looking at? Get inside!

30:41.440 --> 30:42.040
Get down.

30:42.080 --> 30:42.610
Officer,

30:42.640 --> 30:43.500
get out of here.

30:50.280 --> 30:51.360
Go inside.

30:51.560 --> 30:52.560
Go, hurry up.

30:56.760 --> 30:57.560
Hurry inside.

30:58.160 --> 30:59.200
Move it.

31:00.640 --> 31:01.600
Do you want to die?

31:01.600 --> 31:02.360
Go, hurry up.

31:02.400 --> 31:03.280
Behave yourself.

31:03.280 --> 31:04.400
Officer.

31:04.480 --> 31:05.480
Let me out.

31:05.520 --> 31:06.200
Behave.

31:06.560 --> 31:07.360
Officer.

31:07.400 --> 31:07.880
Officer.

31:07.880 --> 31:08.480
Officer.

31:08.560 --> 31:09.480
Stay quiet.

31:09.600 --> 31:11.000
Officer.

31:11.280 --> 31:12.320
What does this mean, officer?

31:12.320 --> 31:13.720
You are not making sense.

31:13.880 --> 31:14.960
Let me out.

31:17.600 --> 31:20.480
Officer,

31:20.520 --> 31:21.400
let me out.

31:50.240 --> 31:51.160
Yueming.

31:52.080 --> 31:52.840
This day

31:52.840 --> 31:56.240
was August 13, 1937.

31:57.760 --> 32:00.320
The Japanese army began massing their naval, land, and air forces

32:00.320 --> 32:02.320
to attack Shanghai.

32:02.320 --> 32:04.800
The Chinese army rose in resistance.

32:04.800 --> 32:07.600
The Battle of Shanghai broke out.

32:08.600 --> 32:09.800
That night,

32:10.040 --> 32:13.000
you kicked Mommy's belly with your little feet.

32:13.360 --> 32:14.690
Mommy was worried about

32:14.800 --> 32:17.060
your father heading to the battlefield.

32:17.400 --> 32:18.680
Aunt Xiaoyue

32:18.720 --> 32:21.450
was still looking forward to her lively wedding.

32:21.960 --> 32:25.200
The cruel war struck

32:25.800 --> 32:27.440
and destroyed all of this.

32:35.680 --> 32:37.240
Change the time on the register.

32:37.240 --> 32:38.160
Just say

32:38.360 --> 32:40.040
they were recruited at the station before.

32:40.040 --> 32:41.640
Whoever talks too much, I'll skin them alive.

32:41.640 --> 32:42.400
Step back.

32:47.280 --> 32:50.000
Everyone, eyes right.

32:52.240 --> 32:53.240
You all know this.

32:53.600 --> 32:55.260
To share the national crisis.

32:55.880 --> 32:57.040
I won't waste words.

32:57.680 --> 32:59.840
The Japanese have already attacked Shanghai.

32:59.840 --> 33:01.240
Our unit is understaffed

33:01.400 --> 33:02.920
and needs to be replenished.

33:02.920 --> 33:05.760
This is a great time for you to serve the country.

33:05.960 --> 33:07.720
Those who stay and serve properly

33:07.720 --> 33:09.800
will each get five dollars as a settlement allowance.

33:09.800 --> 33:11.520
You'll have enough to eat every meal.

33:11.520 --> 33:13.240
From now on, we are brothers.

33:13.320 --> 33:15.880
But let me make it clear up front.

33:16.240 --> 33:17.440
If anyone

33:17.720 --> 33:19.040
tries to play tricks on me

33:19.040 --> 33:20.100
or tries to escape,

33:20.600 --> 33:21.760
don't blame me.

33:23.400 --> 33:24.400
What is that?

33:25.400 --> 33:26.880
What kind of banner are you holding in the room?

33:26.880 --> 33:27.920
Isn't it bad luck?

33:30.960 --> 33:32.620
To share the national crisis.

33:33.400 --> 33:35.600
I've had this intention for a long time.

33:37.560 --> 33:38.360
Sir,

33:38.600 --> 33:41.120
Your face is glowing, and your forehead is bright.

33:41.120 --> 33:42.960
You will surely have great luck soon.

33:42.960 --> 33:44.120
Let me see your left hand.

33:44.120 --> 33:45.000
How old are you?

33:54.840 --> 33:55.680
Don't move.

34:00.080 --> 34:00.920
Fake.

34:01.840 --> 34:02.640
Don't move.

34:11.840 --> 34:14.570
You, go to the back and share the national crisis.

34:15.960 --> 34:16.840
Distribute the uniforms.

34:16.840 --> 34:17.520
Yes, sir.

34:21.639 --> 34:22.280
Yours.

34:23.280 --> 34:24.080
Take it.

34:24.800 --> 34:26.440
I won't wear this ragged skin.

34:26.440 --> 34:27.570
I won't be a soldier.

34:27.639 --> 34:28.440
This is what you call forced conscription.

34:28.440 --> 34:29.370
Do you know that?

34:29.440 --> 34:30.639
What are you yelling for?

34:30.639 --> 34:31.239
No, you...

34:31.480 --> 34:33.280
You guys are worse than bandits.

34:33.480 --> 34:34.639
When bandits kidnap people,

34:34.639 --> 34:36.699
they at least know to notify someone.

34:36.920 --> 34:38.050
I'll let you notify.

34:38.320 --> 34:39.280
I'll kill you.

34:44.880 --> 34:45.679
Captain.

34:45.880 --> 34:46.840
Isn't this the guy who used tofu

34:46.840 --> 34:48.080
to trick us?

34:48.280 --> 34:49.080
Look at him.

34:51.639 --> 34:52.280
Look.

34:53.000 --> 34:54.060
Stand up straight.

34:56.600 --> 34:57.600
An acquaintance.

34:58.360 --> 34:59.200
Let me ask you,

34:59.400 --> 35:02.120
how did you make tofu

35:02.120 --> 35:03.880
taste like beef?

35:04.160 --> 35:05.800
I really thought it was beef.

35:06.240 --> 35:07.840
But then I realized,

35:08.240 --> 35:10.720
the brothers spent money on beef

35:11.040 --> 35:12.440
but ate your tofu.

35:14.760 --> 35:16.400
Sir. Sir.

35:16.480 --> 35:17.940
It's a misunderstanding.

35:18.160 --> 35:19.320
The Manager didn't provide meat.

35:19.320 --> 35:21.160
I'm just a cook, I can't call the shots.

35:21.160 --> 35:21.880
Right?

35:21.920 --> 35:22.640
How about this?

35:22.640 --> 35:24.680
I'll invite you to my wedding feast, okay?

35:24.680 --> 35:26.120
I'm getting married tomorrow.

35:26.120 --> 35:27.080
I'll invite you to my wedding feast.

35:27.080 --> 35:28.200
I beg you, have mercy.

35:28.200 --> 35:29.130
Please let me go.

35:29.160 --> 35:30.280
Please let me go.

35:31.680 --> 35:32.400
Right.

35:33.160 --> 35:34.820
Every cook is responsible for

35:35.200 --> 35:37.080
the rise and fall of the nation.

35:37.480 --> 35:38.410
Did you say that?

35:38.960 --> 35:40.090
Then let me tell you,

35:40.720 --> 35:41.640
you're

35:43.200 --> 35:44.660
definitely a soldier now.

35:45.000 --> 35:45.800
Take it.

35:46.200 --> 35:49.200
Sir, we don't want to be soldiers either.

35:49.640 --> 35:51.570
I'm just a primary school teacher.

35:52.480 --> 35:53.120
Sir,

35:53.160 --> 35:54.090
please spare us.

35:55.280 --> 35:56.280
Sir, please.

35:56.440 --> 35:57.640
I can't fight in a war.

35:57.640 --> 35:58.520
What did I say?

35:58.720 --> 36:01.120
Why don't you understand?

36:01.480 --> 36:03.720
I don't want to be a soldier.

36:04.200 --> 36:06.400
I'm going back to get married tomorrow.

36:08.120 --> 36:08.920
He's anxious.

36:11.080 --> 36:12.140
Teach him a lesson.

36:12.680 --> 36:13.740
Don't hit the face.

36:13.800 --> 36:14.520
Okay.

36:14.680 --> 36:15.240
Go.

36:15.280 --> 36:16.200
What are you doing?

36:16.200 --> 36:18.080
No, what are you doing?

36:18.520 --> 36:19.580
What are you doing?

36:20.160 --> 36:21.490
What are you looking at?

36:25.040 --> 36:26.120
Be a soldier or get married?

36:26.120 --> 36:26.850
Get married.

36:28.320 --> 36:29.850
Be a soldier or get married?

36:30.520 --> 36:31.320
Get married.

36:34.400 --> 36:35.930
Be a soldier or get married?

36:36.200 --> 36:37.120
Get married.

36:38.320 --> 36:39.120
Everyone,

36:40.400 --> 36:41.840
look right!

36:45.760 --> 36:46.690
What did you see?

36:47.040 --> 36:47.800
Nothing.

36:48.680 --> 36:49.880
Didn't see anything.

36:50.040 --> 36:51.240
Didn't see anything.

36:52.720 --> 36:53.980
I saw them hitting him.

36:55.120 --> 36:56.080
Good eyesight.

36:57.800 --> 36:59.400
Only you saw it, right?

36:59.560 --> 37:00.120
Come here.

37:00.120 --> 37:01.180
What are you doing?

37:01.320 --> 37:02.380
What are you doing?

37:02.840 --> 37:03.900
Stand up straight.

37:04.440 --> 37:05.160
You hit people.

37:05.160 --> 37:06.400
Only you saw it.

37:06.480 --> 37:07.480
I'll be a soldier,

37:08.720 --> 37:10.320
but you're bullying people.

37:10.400 --> 37:11.240
Everyone,

37:11.240 --> 37:12.100
Why hit people?

37:12.240 --> 37:14.120
look right!

37:16.600 --> 37:17.560
Cut the crap.

37:18.040 --> 37:18.970
What did you see?

37:19.560 --> 37:21.760
Didn't see anything.

37:21.880 --> 37:22.640
Wrong.

37:23.040 --> 37:24.040
You saw it.

37:24.640 --> 37:27.900
This is called loosening the joints and teaching a lesson.

37:28.120 --> 37:28.960
Understand?

37:29.160 --> 37:31.080
Understood.

37:31.200 --> 37:32.160
What did you see?

37:32.240 --> 37:34.360
Loosening the joints and teaching a lesson.

37:34.360 --> 37:35.120
Louder!

37:35.160 --> 37:37.620
Loosening the joints and teaching a lesson!

37:38.360 --> 37:39.240
Good boy.

37:39.480 --> 37:40.360
That's enough.

37:40.520 --> 37:41.440
Don't kill him.

37:43.080 --> 37:43.880
Pull him over.

37:44.080 --> 37:44.720
Get out of the way.

37:44.720 --> 37:45.840
Come on, go.

37:49.480 --> 37:50.160
Go.

37:58.280 --> 37:59.680
Is the cook responsible?

38:00.320 --> 38:01.120
Responsible.

38:01.560 --> 38:03.090
Be a soldier or get married?

38:04.640 --> 38:05.440
Be a soldier.

38:06.280 --> 38:07.120
Name.

38:08.560 --> 38:09.560
Kong Erbao.

38:09.960 --> 38:10.760
Register.

38:12.800 --> 38:13.640
At ease.

38:15.600 --> 38:16.960
Dress right, dress.

38:18.600 --> 38:19.800
Dress right, dress.

38:22.320 --> 38:23.440
Ready, front.

38:24.880 --> 38:26.080
Brother Fuchen, how have you been?

38:26.080 --> 38:27.210
Is your family well?

38:27.520 --> 38:30.000
All well. Thank you for asking, Brigade Commander.

38:30.000 --> 38:30.840
Salute.

38:35.160 --> 38:36.840
I heard you were assigned to the 87th Brigade.

38:36.840 --> 38:38.240
I've been happy for days.

38:38.480 --> 38:39.840
Commander Liu and Commander Feng

38:39.840 --> 38:41.160
even prepared to line up to welcome you.

38:41.160 --> 38:42.000
I didn't expect you...

38:42.000 --> 38:43.080
Don't say anything yet.

38:43.080 --> 38:44.610
I'll walk around by myself.

38:45.720 --> 38:46.320
Yes, sir.

38:51.600 --> 38:52.760
Left and right turn.

38:54.040 --> 38:55.080
Stop the drill.

38:55.440 --> 38:57.880
Everyone rest for 15 minutes.

39:07.840 --> 39:09.120
Quick, water.

39:09.160 --> 39:09.840
Quick.

39:10.320 --> 39:11.360
You are the only one in a hurry.

39:11.360 --> 39:12.440
Don't rush.

39:14.040 --> 39:15.640
What's the background of our new brigade commander?

39:15.640 --> 39:16.840
What did he do before?

39:16.840 --> 39:17.840
How old is he?

39:47.280 --> 39:48.240
Attention!

40:52.160 --> 40:54.240
Recruit platoon, fall in immediately!

40:54.240 --> 40:55.370
Check your puttees.

40:55.400 --> 40:56.760
Keep your heads clear!

40:57.120 --> 40:58.120
Erbao, what are you doing?

40:58.120 --> 40:59.040
Fall in. Let's go.

40:59.040 --> 40:59.760
Xiazi.

41:00.520 --> 41:01.160
What?

41:02.680 --> 41:03.560
What's wrong?

41:03.640 --> 41:05.160
The new commander will definitely be here soon.

41:05.160 --> 41:05.560
Right.

41:05.640 --> 41:06.770
I just asked around.

41:06.880 --> 41:07.840
Our new brigade commander

41:07.840 --> 41:09.400
used to be a division chief of staff.

41:09.400 --> 41:10.200
He is an intellectual,

41:10.200 --> 41:11.360
strict with discipline, meticulous,

41:11.360 --> 41:12.080
and a tough guy.

41:12.080 --> 41:12.720
Let's go.

41:15.080 --> 41:15.960
The officers

41:16.080 --> 41:17.400
must have gone to the new commander

41:17.400 --> 41:18.730
to present themselves.

41:18.920 --> 41:19.880
This morning,

41:19.880 --> 41:21.520
under the wall of the backyard stables,

41:21.520 --> 41:22.640
I found a dog hole.

41:22.880 --> 41:24.840
There definitely won't be any patrols there now.

41:24.840 --> 41:26.840
There's no better chance than this.

41:26.920 --> 41:27.850
What do you mean?

41:29.320 --> 41:30.800
Nothing ventured, nothing gained.

41:30.800 --> 41:31.760
Are you coming?

41:31.760 --> 41:33.690
You really have it all figured out.

42:50.960 --> 42:52.020
What are you doing?

42:55.680 --> 42:56.610
Bring them over.

43:00.360 --> 43:01.080
Get out.
